    "## 3. Executive Dashboard\n",
    "\n",
    "Recreates the two main visuals from the Module 4 Executive Dashboard wireframe: the\n",
    "**Overall Readiness gauge** and the **Department Scores** bar chart."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
